cards.title: When Dharmendra recalled receiving love from fans, especially women, way too much
cards.abstract: In a 2017 interview with senior journalist and news anchor Rajdeep Sardesai for India Today, Dharmendra humorously noted that women loved him "way too much." He also mentioned that while he appreciated realistic films, he felt today's actors prioritised money and that people were sadly "forgetting their roots."
